he_Five_Key_Elements_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_1000x.png?v=1722007383 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_the_Diffusion_of_Innovations_Theory_The_Five_Key_Elements_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_500x.png?v=1722007383 320w" width="1548" height="1179" alt="Unlocking the Diffusion of Innovations Theory: The Five Key Elements - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Unlocking the Diffusion of Innovations Theory: The Five Key Elements - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-kYHfwS QlfnY pf-159_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-ZOtfp cLnRKw pf-160_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Rawpixel via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-162_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-163_ pf-text-1"><strong>Adoption rate</strong> - Approximately 2.5% of individuals are innovators, 13.5% are early adopters, 34% are early majority, 34% are late majority, and 16% are laggards.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-165_ pf-text-1"><strong>Impact of communication </strong>- Effective communication can accelerate the adoption process by 20-30%.
